# CLIENT 14 — repository-wide ignores.
# The DDNet source tree lives in ddnet/ and carries its own .gitignore for
# build artifacts, executables, generated files, etc. This root file adds
# exclusions for subtrees that must not enter version control:

# Prebuilt external libraries (~400 MB of binaries). Re-fetch via:
#   git clone --depth 1 --shallow-submodules https://github.com/ddnet/ddnet-libs ddnet/ddnet-libs
/ddnet/ddnet-libs/

# Accidental nested clone of upstream ddnet (empty worktree, only a .git).
# Safe to delete entirely to reclaim disk space.
/ddnet/ddnet/

# Reinforce: never track local build output.
/ddnet/build/
